moves.description: Flip a coin until you get tails. This attack does 40 more damage for each heads.

moves.name: Quick Attack
moves.description: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 20 more damage.

moves.name: Buggy Beam
moves.description: Change the type of the next Energy that will be generated for your opponent to 1 of the following at random: {Grass}, {Fire}, {Water}, {Lightning}, {Psychic}, {Fighting}, {Darkness}, or {Metal}.

moves.name: Double Hit
moves.description: Flip 2 coins. This attack does 40 damage for each heads.

moves.name: Pluck
moves.description: Before doing damage, discard all Pokémon Tools from your opponent's Active Pokémon.

moves.name: Clutch
moves.description: During your opponent's next turn, the Defending Pokémon can't retreat.

moves.name: Super Fang
moves.description: Halve your opponent's Active Pokémon's remaining HP, rounded down.

moves.name: Jump Kick
moves.description: This attack also does 20 damage to 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon.

moves.name: Pose
moves.description: Flip a coin. If tails, this attack does nothing.

moves.name: Interrupt
moves.description: Your opponent reveals their hand. Choose a card you find there and shuffle it into your opponent's deck.

moves.name: Fury Attack
moves.description: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 20 damage for each heads.

moves.name: Spin Storm
moves.description: Flip a coin. If heads, put your opponent's Active Pokémon into their hand.

moves.name: Raging Hammer
moves.description: This attack does more damage equal to the damage this Pokémon has on it.

A2-144.name: Skull Fossil
A2-144.description: Play this card as if it were a 40-HP Basic {Colorless} Pokémon.At any time during your turn, you may discard this card from play.This card can't retreat.

A2-145.name: Armor Fossil
A2-145.description: Play this card as if it were a 40-HP Basic {Colorless} Pokémon.At any time during your turn, you may discard this card from play.This card can't retreat.

A2-146.name: Pokémon Communication
A2-146.description: Choose a Pokémon in your hand and switch it with a random Pokémon in your deck.

A2-147.name: Giant Cape
A2-147.description: The Pokémon this card is attached to gets +20 HP.

A2-148.name: Rocky Helmet
A2-148.description: If the Pokémon this card is attached to is in the Active Spot and is damaged by an attack from your opponent's Pokémon, do 20 damage to the Attacking Pokémon.

A2-149.name: Lum Berry
A2-149.description: At the end of each turn, if the Pokémon this card is attached to is affected by any Special Conditions, it recovers from all of them, and discard this card.

A2-150.name: Cyrus
A2-150.description: Switch in 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon that has damage on it to the Active Spot.

A2-151.name: Team Galactic Grunt
A2-151.description: Put 1 random Glameow, Stunky, or Croagunk from your deck into your hand.

A2-152.name: Cynthia
A2-152.description: During this turn, attacks used by your Garchomp or Togekiss do +50 damage to your opponent's Active Pokémon.

A2-153.name: Volkner
A2-153.description: Choose 1 of your Electivire or Luxray. Attach 2 {Lightning} Energy from your discard pile to that Pokémon.

A2-154.name: Dawn
A2-154.description: Move an Energy from 1 of your Benched Pokémon to your Active Pokémon.

A2-155.name: Mars
A2-155.description: Your opponent shuffles their hand into their deck and draws a card for each of their remaining points needed to win.
